    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my favorite set of wheels. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape\u2014honestly, it drives like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road for many more adventures. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
