    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with this beauty, and it has been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and consistently maintained, so you can count on a smooth trip every time you get behind the wheel. It has a few minor signs of character as you'd expect, but it's super clean and runs like a dream. I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
