    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes an individual throttle body setup for instantaneous response, delivering its peak output at a visceral 8,300 RPM. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast shifts, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This specimen has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The suspension retains its factory-tuned kinematics with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) offering variable damping rates. The chassis remains rigid, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback missing from modern EPS systems. Finished with a clean underside and healthy bushings, this M3 is optimized for the purist seeking a balance of mechanical transparency and GT capability.",
